---
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Logo from '../../public/Duckie.jpg';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import MobileMenu from '../containers/MobileMenu.astro';
---

<html lang='en'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='utf-8' />
    <link rel='icon' type='image/svg+xml' href='/Duckie.jpg' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width' />
    <meta name='generator' content={Astro.generator} />
    <title>Duckie | The coolest Duck on Solana</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <MobileMenu />
    <section class='min-h-screen bg-yellow-200 p-14 md:p-24'>
      <section class='flex items-center justify-center gap-20 flex-wrap'>
        <div
          class='lg:w-1/2 px-10 py-20 bg-yellow-400 rounded-3xl'
        >
          <h2 class='text-white font-customFont text-6xl'>Meet</h2>
          <h1 class='font-customFont text-white'>Duckie</h1>
          <!-- <p class='mt-12 text-xl text-white'>
            <span class='font-customFont'>Duckie</span> is the next big memecoin that
            combines the charm of everyone's favorite animal, the Duck, with the
            energy of memecoins. With a community-driven approach and a focus on
            fun, <span class='font-customFont'>Duckie</span> is poised to become the
            coolest memecoin on the market.
          </p> -->
          <p class="mt-2 text-xl text-white">
            The most quack-tacular memecoin. A duck with attitude soaring high in the crypto world! Fun, community, and pure feathered chaos. The time of "croak" is over, it's time to "quack"
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class='md:w/1-2'>
          <Image
            src={Logo}
            alt='logo'
            class='bg-white rounded-full border-8 w-96 border-yellow-500'
          />
        </div>
      </section>
    </section>
    <section
      id='about'
      class='bg-yellow-400 w-full min-h-screen border-t border-yellow-500 py-16 px-10 md:px-24'
    >
      <h3 class='text-white font-customFont text-center'>About</h3>
      <p class='text-white text-xl my-24'>
        <span class='font-customFont'>Duckie Coin</span> is a fresh, community-driven
        memecoin that blends the lovable charm of Ducks with the dynamic energy
        of cryptocurrency. Designed to bring both fun and opportunity to the crypto
        space, Duckie isn't just another coin—it's a movement. Our mission is simple:
        build a lighthearted, inclusive community where everyone can participate
        in the journey of financial growth, all while having a blast.
        <br />
        <br />
        With our adorable yet cheeky Duck mascot, <span
          class='font-customFont'>Duckie Coin</span
        > aims to be a symbol of resilience and adaptability, much like the Duck
        itself. Whether you're new to crypto or a seasoned trader, Duckie offers a
        chance to join a project that doesn’t take itself too seriously while still
        offering serious potential.
        <br />
        <br />

        <span class='font-customFont'>Duckie</span> is more than just a token—it's
        an experience, a meme, and a growing community. We believe that the future
        of crypto is not just about technology, but also about fun, creativity, and
        connection. So whether you're here to hodl or just along for the Duck-powered
        ride,
        <span class='font-customFont'>Duckie Coin</span> is your ticket to the coolest
        crypto adventure around.
        <br />
        <br />

        Join us and start waddling towards a brighter, meme-fueled future!
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class='min-h-screen bg-yellow-200 p-10 md:p-24' id='how-to-buy'>
      <h3 class='font-customFont text-white text-center'>How to buy</h3>

      <div class='my-20 flex flex-col gap-10'>
        <article
          class='w-full flex items-center justify-start gap-10 flex-wrap md:flex-nowrap text-white bg-yellow-400 rounded-lg border-2 border-yellow-500 p-10 text-lg'
        >
          <img
            src='https://187760183-files.gitbook.io/~/files/v0/b/gitbook-x-prod.appspot.com/o/spaces%2F-MVOiF6Zqit57q_hxJYp%2Ficon%2FU7kNZ4ygz4QW1rUwOuTT%2FWhite%20Ghost_docs_nu.svg?alt=media&token=447b91f6-db6d-4791-902d-35d75c19c3d1'
            class='w-28 rounded-full'
          />

          <div>
            <h2 class='text-white font-customFont text-4xl'>
              Download Phantom Wallet
            </h2>
            <p>
              Metamask is one of the most popular crypto wallets on the market.
              You can download it on IOS and Adroid or you can even download the
              browser extension and become part of the Solana ecosystem.
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article
          class='w-full flex items-center justify-center gap-10 flex-wrap md:flex-nowrap text-white bg-yellow-400 rounded-lg border-2 border-yellow-500 p-10 text-lg'
        >
          <img
            src='/solana.webp'
            class='w-28'
          />

          <div>
            <h2 class='text-white font-customFont text-4xl'>
              Get some <span>$SOL</span>
            </h2>
            <p>
              Once you have your Metamasl Wallet installed and setup, it's time
              to get some $SOL to start trading. You can buy some $SOL at
              your favourite CEX and transfer it to your Metamask Wallet to
              start trading.
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article
          class='w-full flex items-center justify-center gap-10 flex-wrap md:flex-nowrap text-white bg-yellow-400 rounded-lg border-2 border-yellow-500 p-10 text-lg'
        >
        <img
        src='https://research.binance.com/static/images/projects/raydium/logo.png'
        class='w-28 rounded-full'
      />

          <div>
            <h2 class='text-white font-customFont text-4xl'>
              Go to Raydium
            </h2>
            <p>
              Once you have $SOL on your Metamask Wallet, it's time to trade
              it for some $Duckie. To do that, you can go to our Raydium liquidity pool
              <!-- <a
                class='text-yellow-600 underline font-bold'
                href='https://pump.fun/HZhBACLZxwRbecoHsiqmbQeFha3kzWeJWXkEBDfGpump'
                >Click here</a
              > -->
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article
          class='w-full flex items-center justify-center gap-10 flex-wrap md:flex-nowrap text-white bg-yellow-400 rounded-lg border-2 border-yellow-500 p-10 text-lg'
        >
          <img src='/Duckie.jpg' class='w-28 rounded-full border-4 border-yellow-600' />

          <div>
            <h2 class='text-white font-customFont text-4xl'>
              Exchange <span>$SOL</span> for $Duckie
            </h2>
            <p>
              You can trade some $SOL for $Duckie. We have ZERO taxes so you
              don’t need to worry about buying with a specific slippage,
              although you may need to use slippage during times of market
              volatility.
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section
      id='why-duckie'
      class='bg-yellow-400 w-full min-h-screen border-t border-yellow-500 py-16 px-10 md:px-24'
    >
      <h3 class='text-white font-customFont text-center'>Why Duckie?</h3>

      <ul class='my-16 flex flex-col gap-10'>
        <li class='text-2xl md:text-5xl text-white font-customFont list-disc'>
          <b class='underline'>Community-Driven:</b> Duckie Coin is built by and for
          its community, focusing on fun and inclusivity. Joining early means becoming
          part of a passionate and growing community.
        </li>

        <li class='text-2xl md:text-5xl text-white font-customFont list-disc'>
          <b class='underline'>Fun & Lighthearted:</b> Duckie brings a unique, meme-inspired
          approach to crypto with its playful Duck mascot, making it more than
          just an investment—it's an enjoyable experience.
        </li>

        <li class='text-2xl md:text-5xl text-white font-customFont list-disc'>
          <b class='underline'>Low Entry Price:</b> With an affordable entry point,
          Duckie allows new investors to get in on the ground floor with the potential
          for significant returns as the coin gains traction.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section
      class='min-h-screen bg-yellow-200 py-16 px-10 md:px-24'
      id='tokenomics'
    >
      <h5 class='font-customFont text-white text-center'>Tokenomics</h5>

      <div class='flex justify-between items-center flex-col md:flex-row'>
        <div class='md:w-2/3 flex flex-col items-center'>
          <article
            class='w-full flex items-center justify-start gap-4 flex-wrap md:flex-nowrap text-white bg-yellow-400 rounded-lg border-2 border-yellow-500 p-10 text-lg my-12 flex-col md:mt-24'
          >
            <h5 class='font-customFont text-5xl'>Total Supply:</h5>
            <h5 class='font-customFont text-4xl text-center'>
              1,000,000,000 $Duckie
            </h5>
          </article>

          <article
            class='w-full flex items-center justify-start gap-4 flex-wrap text-wrap md:flex-nowrap text-white bg-yellow-400 rounded-lg border-2 border-yellow-500 p-10 text-lg flex-col'
          >
            <h5 class='font-customFont text-5xl'>Token address:</h5>
            <h5
              class='font-customFont text-lg text-center md:text-4xl text-wrap'
            >
            mntDf2RuNsgwZNBJjK5cwCdFX<br />eEXANTfKLwAqDXsr51
            </h5>
          </article>
        </div>

        <img src='/Duckie.jpg' class=' rounded-full md:w-1/3 h-full lg:mt-20 lg:ml-10' />
      </div>
    </section>

    
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>

<style is:global>
  * {
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
  }

  @font-face {
    font-family: 'Funny Sunshine';
    src: url('/fonts/FUNNY SUNSHINE.woff') format('woff');
    font-weight: normal;
    font-style: normal;
    font-display: swap;
  }

  h1,
  h3,
  h4 {
    font-size: 10rem;
    line-height: 8rem;
    stroke: yellow;
    text-shadow:
      2px 0 #e5b400,
      -2px 0 #e5b400,
      0 2px #e5b400,
      0 -2px #e5b400,
      1px 1px #e5b400,
      -1px -1px #e5b400,
      1px -1px #e5b400,
      -1px 1px #e5b400;
  }

  h5 {
    font-size: 10rem;
    line-height: 8rem;
    stroke: yellow;
    text-shadow:
      2px 0 #e5b400,
      -2px 0 #e5b400,
      0 2px #e5b400,
      0 -2px #e5b400,
      1px 1px #e5b400,
      -1px -1px #e5b400,
      1px -1px #e5b400,
      -1px 1px #e5b400;
  }

  h2,
  span,
  li {
    text-shadow:
      2px 0 #e5b400,
      -2px 0 #e5b400,
      0 2px #e5b400,
      0 -2px #e5b400,
      1px 1px #e5b400,
      -1px -1px #e5b400,
      1px -1px #e5b400,
      -1px 1px #e5b400;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
    h1,
    h3 {
      font-size: 7rem;
      text-wrap: wrap;
    }

    h5 {
      font-size: 5rem;
      text-wrap: wrap;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 380px) {
    h1,
    h3 {
      font-size: 6rem;
      text-wrap: wrap;
    }

    h5 {
      font-size: 4rem;
      text-wrap: wrap;
    }
  }
</style>
